strapiEvent.name: Design Panel Discussion
strapiEvent.location: NABOR Event Center 314 N. Goad Springs St. Lowell
strapiEvent.description: Join Kristen Payne - VP/GM with Better Homes and Gardens magazine as she shares insight of what's hot for 2023. Then there will be an open panel session where you can ask your burning questions to a group of local designers, real estate agents and builders. Invite friends and favorite clients! PLEASE RSVP
